Here&#x27;s one possible implementation of valueOf:<p><pre><code>  import numpy as np

  def valueOf(*v):
    return sum( v * np.power(10,range(len(v)))[::-1] )

  > valueOf( 2,3,4 )  # => 234

</code></pre>
